However, I value objectivity and rationality highly, and I tend to rely on facts and data to inform my decisions rather than relying solely on emotions.

I also tend to be quite particular about who I let into my inner circle, and I may be hesitant to make new friends due to my tendency to be reserved and cautious.

While I understand the importance of interpretation and analysis in understanding the context and meaning of creative works, I tend to prioritize clarity and predictability in my own thinking and decision-making. I prefer to rely on logical reasoning and evidence-based analysis rather than relying on personal opinions or emotions.

While I can appreciate the appeal of open-ended endings that encourage interpretation, I tend to prefer media that provides a clear resolution and a sense of closure.
